0: The Cathedral of Jesus Saviour of the World

--------------------
Text: The Cathedral of Jesus Saviour of the World (Albanian: "Katedralja e Jezusi i Vetmi Shpëtimtar i Botës" , also Catholic Cathedral of Rrëshen) is a religious building affiliated with the Catholic church that functions as the cathedral of Rrëshen.
